1.12.20  11:51 am   I write music, but I'm not entirely sure why. I know I've got a drive for it and I love listening to music, but anytime I try to think about why I'm an artist who creates I feel like I don't actually have an answer or reason (compared to say artists I know who craft stories with drawings and comics and such).

      Is it enough for me to just have an urge to compose with no understanding why,

     or do I need to work out why I do what I do?
